<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="terribly-adv">terribly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'terəbli/    美 /'terəbli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[口语] 非常；很：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Oh, I’m terribly sorry about that.
哦，对那件事我很抱歉。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was terribly excited on the morning of that day as customers began arriving.
那天早晨客人们陆续到达，他很兴奋。</p><footer>2009 天津</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>可怕地；惊人地</strong></h4></div>